FadeInDistanceStart:
The FadeInDistance at which to start hearing this sound.
       * If you want to hear the sound up close then setting this to 0 might be a good option.
FadeInDistanceEnd: The distance at which this sound has faded in completely.
FadeOutDistanceStart: The distance at which this sound starts fading out.
FadeOutDistanceEnd: The distance at which this sound is no longer audible.
Volume: The volume for which this Input should be played.
